// SMT (Satisfiability Modulo Theories) solver integration for formal verification:
// - SMT-LIB2 format generation
// - Z3/CVC5 solver backends
// - Theory support (bitvectors, arrays, reals, integers)
// - Model extraction and counterexample generation
